<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>A股捡垃圾</title>
    <meta name="description" content="A股捡垃圾：聚焦A股长期投资、红利策略与价值投资。提供股息率、分红历史、ROE、PE/PB估值与历史分位、价格分位、行业分类与多维筛选，辅助构建稳健的投资组合。">
    <meta name="keywords" content="A股,红利,高股息,股息率,分红,分红历史,价值投资,长期投资,ROE,PE,PB,估值,估值分位,价格分位,选股,行业分类,财务指标,股票分析">
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" type="image/svg+xml">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        .table-container {
            overflow-x: auto;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 text-gray-900">
    <nav class="bg-blue-600 text-white shadow-lg p-4">
        <div class="<%= @layout_full_width ? 'w-full' : 'container mx-auto' %> flex justify-between items-center px-3 sm:px-6">
            <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3 hover:text-blue-100">
                <img src="/logo.svg" alt="A股捡垃圾" class="w-8 h-8">
                <div class="flex flex-col">
                    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-tight">A股捡垃圾</h1>
                </div>
            </a>
            <div class="space-x-4">
                <a href="/" class="hover:text-blue-200">股票列表</a>
                <a href="/indices" class="hover:text-blue-200">指数</a>
                <a href="/etfs" class="hover:text-blue-200">ETF</a>
                <a href="/macro" class="hover:text-blue-200">宏观</a>
                <a href="/kb" class="hover:text-blue-200">知识库</a>
                <% if logged_in? %>
                    <a href="/pools" class="hover:text-blue-200">股票池</a>
                    <span class="text-blue-200 text-sm"><%= current_user.email %></span>
                    <form action="/logout" method="post" class="inline">
                        <button type="submit" class="hover:text-blue-200 text-sm">退出</button>
                    </form>
                <% else %>
                    <a href="/login" class="hover:text-blue-200">登录</a>
                    <a href="/signup" class="hover:text-blue-200">注册</a>
                <% end %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="<%= @layout_full_width ? 'w-full' : 'container mx-auto' %> px-3 py-6 sm:px-6">
        <% if flash %>
            <div class="mb-4 px-4 py-3 rounded border border-yellow-200 bg-yellow-50 text-yellow-900 text-sm"><%= flash %></div>
        <% end %>
        <%= yield %>
    </main>

    <footer class="mt-12 p-6 text-center text-gray-500 border-t border-gray-200">
        <p>&copy; 2026 A股捡垃圾</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
